\b 29. ______ 
\b0 Begin 
\b Phone Follow-Up on 1st R\'e9sum\'e9s
\b0 . Begin to schedule interviews. Remember how critical this is. Your statistical odds of getting a job offer just from sending out r\'e9sum\'e9s is 1 out of 254. Add an actual phone contact to that, and it jumps to 1 out of 15!. You are better off to send out 35 resumes and to follow-up than to send out 1000 where all you do is wait. Prepare to do great phone follow up calls with each of these resumes.\

