\b 31. ________ 
\b0 From now on focus totally on what you are moving 
\b TO
\b0 , not what you are moving 
\b FROM
\b0 . Focusing on what you are coming 
\b FROM 
\b0 tends to keep anger, resentment, bitterness, discouragement and frustration high. Getting clear on what you are going 
\b TO 
\b0 will release hope, optimism, boldness and enthusiasm.\

