\b 47. _______ 
\b0 Take a millionaire to lunch today. You will be surprised how available he/she is. Share that you are on a new path and just want their advice. Some people may be telling you that you can\'92t do what you want to do. But a millionaire will encourage you to reach for your dreams. One of the hallmark characteristics of successful people is that they spend time with those people already performing at high levels. And be sure to pick up the tab for lunch.\

\b 48. 
\b0 _____ Make your final plan \'96 and BEGIN -- AND DON\'92T LOOK BACK FOR ONE YEAR. You must be committed. If you don\'92t totally believe in what you are doing, no one else will. Commit to the focused, fulfilling, and directed choice. See this as the next \'93season\'94 of your life.\

\i\b And congratulations on making the choices for fulfilling, meaningful \'96 and profitable \'96 work!\
